genresAdvancedInfo.name: pune indie
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Pune indie is a genre of music originating from the city of Pune, India. It features a blend of indie rock, pop, and folk music, often incorporating traditional Indian instruments such as the tabla and sitar. Pune indie artists often sing in both English and Hindi, with lyrics that explore themes of love, identity, and social issues.
